Title: etherbox.temp: Now supports lower levels, output configurable to Celsius, Fahrenheit or Kelvin
Level: 1
Component: checks
Compatible: incomp
Version: 1.2.7i1
Date: 1418915146
Class: feature

etherbox.temp now no longer uses the room temperature WATO rule, but the new "temperature" rule, note that the
old rule no longer applies to etherbox. The new rule allows to set lower levels, as well as output in
Celsius, Fahrenheit or Kelvin.
